\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/evora\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Evora<\/a> (about 2.5 hours into your journey).<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rent a car here<\/a> or learn <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/travel-portugal-campervan\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">how to travel Portugal by campervan<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085043\/evora4-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"portugal aesthetic\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"portugal aesthetic\" class=\"wp-image-55782 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085043\/evora4-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085043\/evora4-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085043\/evora4-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085043\/evora4-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085043\/evora4-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\