\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-wine-tour-portugal\">Wine Tour Portugal<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Make sure to book one of the many wine tours on offer in the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/douro-valley-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Douro Valley<\/a>. Wine tours range from tastings to learning about the harvesting experience or staying the night on one of the beautiful estates.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Here&#x2019;s <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/douro-valley-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">how to visit the Douro Valley<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084935\/douro-valley2-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"douro valley portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"douro valley portugal\" class=\"wp-image-55768 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084935\/douro-valley2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084935\/douro-valley2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084935\/douro-val