on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22163405\/portugal-travel-itinerary-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22163405\/portugal-travel-itinerary-349x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Road Trip Portugal: The Perfect 3-week Itinerary\" height=\"600\" width=\"349\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-peneda-geres-national-park-portugal\">Peneda Geres National Park, Portugal<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have time, drive a little further north to Peneda Geres National Park&#x2019;s remote landscapes. Here you will find many waterfalls, lakes, and deep valleys, peppered with quaint hillside villages and Roman ruins. The largest national park in Portugal is well worth the trip if you are <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/travel-portugal-campervan\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">traveling Portugal by campervan<\/a>, as it&#x2019;s the ideal way to explore nature.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18092445\/braga-portugal.jpg\" alt=\"portugal road trip braga\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"portugal road trip braga\" class=\"wp-image-56052 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-src