ntent\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085410\/porto1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-day-10-11-arouca-and-aveiro\">Day 10-11: Arouca and Aveiro<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Arouca Paiva Walkways is an 8km long stretch of stairs and boardwalks that scale the rocks and valley surrounding the river Paiva. If visiting in the summer, there are also deep pools in certain areas that are suitable for swimming. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip.jpg\" alt=\"Arouca portugal road trip\"><\/noscript><img width=\"440\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Arouca portugal road trip\" class=\"wp-image-56159 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-782x600.jpg 782w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-1055x810.jpg 1055w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-440x338.jpg 440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-163x125.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-234x180.jpg 234w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-768x590.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-1024x786.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-1407x1080.jpg 1407w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-1876x1440.jpg 1876w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-300x230.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-600x461.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22084308\/Arouca-portugal-road-trip.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><figcaption>Source: Unsplash<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>It is a fairly steep and difficult walk that takes around 2 hours 30 mins. Because of this, you&#x2019;ll need to wear proper walking shoes, bring a hat, and lots of water if walking in the summer. The fast-flowing river also makes it an excellent place for kayakers who want to enjoy the white water and rapids.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Porto to Arouca<\/strong>: 50 minutes driving from Porto. Alternatively, take a taxi or join an organized tour leaving from the city.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Spend the day here hiking, before driving on to the town of Aveiro to spend the night.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2.jpg\" alt=\"aveiro portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"aveiro portugal\" class=\"wp-image-56042 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083212\/aveiro2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-aveiro\"><strong>Aveiro<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Wake up on day 11 in the unique town of Aveiro, known as &#x2018;the Venice of Portugal&#x2019;, with its colorful houses, canals, and brightly painted gondolas. Spend the day in Aveiro lazily, floating along the canals that feed away from the Aveiro lagoon. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/best-places-to-visit-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best Places to visit in Portugal<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"portugal colorful houses\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"portugal colorful houses\" class=\"wp-image-56047 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4.jpg 1281w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083233\/aveiro4-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figur