oads\/2021\/04\/18083223\/aveiro3-300x391.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083223\/aveiro3-600x782.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083223\/aveiro3-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083223\/aveiro3.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The gondolas of Aveiro are called &#x2018;Moliceiros&#x2019;, and most of the guides that row these boats will also provide you with interesting historical information about the maritime town.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Arouca to Aveiro:<\/strong> 1 hr 20 minutes by car. If you are using public transport, it&#x2019;s easiest to go back to Porto and transfer onto a train from there.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Discover Italy:<\/strong>&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/venice\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best things to do in Venice, Italy!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado.jpg\" alt=\"beach portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"beach portugal\" class=\"wp-image-56049 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/18083244\/Costa-Nova-do-Prado-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" on