opener\">Bucket list Things To Do in the Algarve<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5.jpg\" alt=\"portugal travel beaches\"><\/noscript><img width=\"286\" height=\"338\" alt=\"portugal travel beaches\" class=\"wp-image-55794 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1624px) 100vw, 1624px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5.jpg 1624w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-508x600.jpg 508w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-685x810.jpg 685w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-286x338.jpg 286w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-25x30.jpg 25w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-138x163.jpg 138w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-152x180.jpg 152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-650x768.jpg 650w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-866x1024.jpg 866w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-914x1080.jpg 914w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-1218x1440.jpg 1218w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-300x355.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-600x709.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085143\/lagos5-25x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinour