el=\"noopener\">the things to do in Albufeira<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"carvoeiro portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"carvoeiro portugal\" class=\"wp-image-55762 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16084905\/Carvoeiro2.jpg 1281w\" tempsrc