   <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Good to know:<\/strong> Faro airport is located only 10 minutes drive from the town itself and there is a regular airport shuttle bus that departs throughout the day.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Lagos to Faro:<\/strong> Direct train in 1 hour 45 minutes OR drive in less than an hour.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22090641\/portugal-travel-aesthetic.jpg\" alt=\"portugal travel aesthetic\"><\/noscript><img width=\"251\" height=\"338\" alt=\"portugal travel aesthetic\" class=\"wp-image-56174 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1423px) 100vw, 1423px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22090641\/portugal-travel-aesthetic.jpg 1423w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22090641\/portugal-travel-aesthetic-445x600.jpg 445w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22090641\/portugal-travel-aesthetic-600x810.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22090641\/portugal-travel-aesthetic-251x338.jpg 251w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22090641\/portugal-travel-aesthetic-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22090641\/portugal-travel-aesthetic-121x163.jpg 121w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/22090641\/portugal-travel-aesthetic-133x180.jpg 133w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-co